  "id": "runeforgestudio-velnathis",
  "title": "RuneForge Studio: Vel'Nathis & The Shard",
  "description": "<p>A self-contained psychological horror story engine for D&D 5e. Includes Vel'Nathis (Tiny Fiend, CR 4) — a bound demon who communicates with carriers of his obsidian prison shard through nightly dreams — the Shard of Vel'Nathis (Very Rare cursed loot item with DC 14 WIS save and 1/dawn use), a 1d10 Compulsion Table with full mechanical consequences, and a structured GM Journal with lore, escalation track, NPC reference, and story hooks.</p><p>Tier 2–3 content (player levels 5–10). Designed for multi-session deployment.</p>",
